How to make tea

Locate the tea bag
Locate the teacup/mug
Locate the water kettle
Locate the condiments (sugar, milk, honey…etc.)
Pour water (from either faucet or water bottle) into the kettle
Turn the kettle on
Allow the kettle to warm the water
Once the kettle signifies that the water is ready, pour the water into the teacup/mug
Take the tea bag in place it in the hot water
Let the teabag steep in the hot water for 2 minutes
Take the tea bag out and throw way 
Pour in desired condiments (sugar, milk, honey…etc.) and stir everything together
Drink!
